            <scopecontent id="aspace_b017aca7ea162c167376b6609a34a40b">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Arranged alphabetically, the series includes clippings, correspondence, photographs, and writings. Biographical materials include an application for the American Bar Association's Lawyer Placement Information Service, completed by Atkins in the 1960s, which provides details about his career. The photographs are of Atkins during his time at Yale Law School.</p>
            </scopecontent>
